{"tid":1760881,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"2020日本櫻花旅行","createTime":"2019-11-28T13:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T12:35:54.000Z","uid":199985,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf0733670e042413d1253da325d184eb1cd0864","tid":1760881,"uid":199985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就想下年3月頭至3月中/4月尾打後<br />\n帶兩老返鄉下睇吓櫻花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下大家有冇邊d地方好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋有啲咩要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近年櫻花好似多數早左開？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪應該3月頭至3月中去好啲？<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">不過兩老就好鬼麻煩唔肯自遊行 <br />\n我又冇車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以要跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未睇過今年終於有假可以去見識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"cfc1b3d92264bcc48976a7e992723d0ef649d718","tid":1760881,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:51:22.000Z","msg":"你做導遊"},{"pid":"952afaab72ef54bdcb0cbc2fd28c2937619920d2","tid":1760881,"uid":8122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:51:26.000Z","msg":"櫻花通常係3月尾-4月頭盛開"},{"pid":"8b47630c9332c7e7868e078b8ee1670ce22afeba","tid":1760881,"uid":44277,"l